	"KIRLIA used TOXIC!"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePikeRoomNormal_Text_KirliaUsedHypnosis {
	"KIRLIA used HYPNOSIS!"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePikeRoomNormal_Text_KirliaUsedThunderWave {
	"KIRLIA used THUNDER WAVE!"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePikeRoomNormal_Text_KirliaUsedWillOWisp {
	"KIRLIA used WILL-O-WISP!"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePikeRoomNormal_Text_DusclopsUsedWillOWisp {
	"DUSCLOPS used WILL-O-WISP!"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePikeRoomNormal_Text_DusclopsUsedIceBeam {
	"DUSCLOPS used ICE BEAM!"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePikeRoomNormal_Text_ThatsEnough {
	"Look here!
	That's quite enough!"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePikeRoomNormal_Text_ApologizeForKirlia {
	"I must apologize to you…

	My KIRLIA has a TIMID nature…"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePikeRoomNormal_Text_ApologizeForDusclops {
	"I must apologize to you…

	My DUSCLOPS has a TIMID nature…"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePikeRoomNormal_Text_AttacksWhenStartled {
	"It attacks without warning if it is
	startled by another person…

	Are you and your POKéMON all right?"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePikeRoomNormal_Text_ApologizeHopeMonsAreFine {
	"I do apologize for what happened…
	I do hope your POKéMON are fine."
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePikeRoomNormal_Text_Silence {
	"… … … … … …
	… … … … … …"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePikeRoomNormal_Text_BattleSomewhatToughTrainer {
	"Welcome…

	Here, we will have you battle
	a somewhat-tough TRAINER…"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePikeRoomNormal_Text_RestoreToFullHealth {
	"How wonderful…

	To honor your victory, your POKéMON
	shall be restored to full health…"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePikeRoomNormal_Text_EnjoyRestOfChallenge2 {
	"I urge you to enjoy the rest of your
	Battle Choice challenge…"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePikeRoomNormal_Text_ImThePikeQueen {
	"I am LUCY…
	I am the law here…
	For I am the PIKE QUEEN…

	You already know it, but to advance,
	you must defeat me…

	…I'm not one for idle chatter.
	Hurry. Come on…"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePikeRoomNormal_Text_HopeYouDidntUseUpLuck {
	"Your luck…
	I hope you didn't use it all up here…"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePikeRoomNormal_Text_LucyShowMeFrontierPass {
	"{SPEAKER NAME_LUCY}… … … … … …
	Show me your FRONTIER PASS…"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePikeRoomNormal_Text_ReceivedLuckSymbol {
	"The Luck Symbol was embossed on
	the FRONTIER PASS!"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePikeRoomNormal_Text_AllThereIsDisappear {
	"…That's all there is…
	Disappear already…"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePikeRoomNormal_Text_LucyYouAgain {
	"{SPEAKER NAME_LUCY}…You again…

	… … … … … …

	…I've trampled flowers and braved
	storms to get to where I am…

	I don't feel any compulsion to keep
	losing to the same opponent…

	… … … … … …
	Fine… I'll do it…"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePikeRoomNormal_Text_NowComeOn {
	"Now!
	Come on!"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePikeRoomNormal_Text_LucyFrontierPass {
	"{SPEAKER NAME_LUCY}… … … … … …

	…FRONTIER PASS…"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePikeRoomNormal_Text_LuckSymbolTookGoldenShine {
	"The Luck Symbol took on
	a golden shine!"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePikeRoomNormal_Text_IWontForget {
	"…You, I won't forget…
	…Ever…"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePikeRoomNormal_Text_ChoseRoomNoHeal {
	"I welcome you…

	Giggle…
	You seem to be bereft of luck…

	If only you hadn't chosen this room,
	your POKéMON could have been healed…"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePikeRoomNormal_Text_ChoseRoomHealOne {
	"I welcome you…

	Since you have chosen this room, I will
	restore one POKéMON to full health…"
}

text BattleFrontier_BattlePikeRoomNormal_Text_ChoseRoomHealTwo {
	"I welcome you…

	Since you have chosen this room, I will
	restore two POKéMON to full health…"
}

